EGRET package includes WRTDS and flowHistory

Details

Collection of functions to do WRTDS and flowHistory analysis, and produce graphs and tables of data and results from these analyses.

References

Hirsch, R.M., and De Cicco, L.A., 2014, User guide to Exploration and Graphics for RivEr Trends (EGRET) and dataRetrieval: R packages for hydrologic data: U.S. Geological Survey Techniques and Methods book 4, chap. A10, 94 p., https://doi.org/10.3133/tm4A10
